+	/*
+	 * The caller should hold either p->pi_lock or rq->lock, when changing
+	 * a task's CPU. ->pi_lock for waking tasks, rq->lock for runnable tasks.
+	 *
+	 * Furthermore, all task_rq users should acquire both locks, see
+	 * task_rq_lock().
